data.description: Welcome to this charming two-bedroom, two-bathroom home located in the desirable F Childers subdivision. Situated on a lovely .788 acres and offers 1,500 square feet of living space. As you enter the home, you are welcomed by a bright and airy living room with beamed ceilings and plenty of natural light. The living room opens to the dining room. The kitchen is equipped with a built-in oven and microwave, and plenty of counter space for meal prep. The master bedroom is spacious and features a large closet and an en-suite bathroom with 2 separate vanities. The second bedroom is also nice sized and perfect for a guest room or office. In addition to the two bedrooms, the home also features an added jacuzzi room, perfect for relaxing after a long day. The jacuzzi room could also be converted into an office space or extra room. The laundry room is conveniently located off the kitchen and provides plenty of storage. Outside, the home features an unattached large two-car garage with a carport attached. The backyard is fenced for privacy and perfect for outdoor entertaining. This home is a must-see! With its generous lot size, two bedrooms, two bathrooms, added jacuzzi room, beamed ceilings, large two-car garage with carport attached, laundry room, master bathroom with two separate vanities, built-in oven and microwave, and privacy fence, this home is sure to please. Don’t miss out on this opportunity to call this your home!
